# Multi-Timeframe Analysis Flow Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    Start([Analysis Request]) --> Type{Trading Type?}

    Type --> |Scalping| ScalpTF[Select Timeframes<br/>M1, M5, M15]
    Type --> |Day Trading| DayTF[Select Timeframes<br/>M15, H1, H4]
    Type --> |Swing Trading| SwingTF[Select Timeframes<br/>H4, D1, W1]
    Type --> |Position| PosTF[Select Timeframes<br/>D1, W1, MN1]

    ScalpTF --> Cache{Cache Valid?<br/>5 sec for scalping}
    DayTF --> Cache2{Cache Valid?<br/>30 sec for day}
    SwingTF --> Cache3{Cache Valid?<br/>1 hour for swing}
    PosTF --> Cache4{Cache Valid?<br/>1 day for position}

    Cache --> |Yes| UseCache[Use Cached Analysis]
    Cache --> |No| Fetch[Fetch Fresh Data]

    Cache2 --> |Yes| UseCache
    Cache2 --> |No| Fetch
    Cache3 --> |Yes| UseCache
    Cache3 --> |No| Fetch
    Cache4 --> |Yes| UseCache
    Cache4 --> |No| Fetch

    Fetch --> Parallel[Parallel Timeframe Analysis]

    subgraph MTF["Multi-Timeframe Parallel Processing"]
        direction LR
        TF1[Lower TF<br/>Entry Signals]
        TF2[Mid TF<br/>Confluence]
        TF3[Higher TF<br/>Trend Filter]
    end

    Parallel --> TF1
    Parallel --> TF2
    Parallel --> TF3

    TF1 --> Analyze1[Analyze<br/>Zones & Patterns]
    TF2 --> Analyze2[Analyze<br/>Trend & Structure]
    TF3 --> Analyze3[Analyze<br/>Overall Trend]

    Analyze1 --> Score1[Score: 35%]
    Analyze2 --> Score2[Score: 40%]
    Analyze3 --> Score3[Score: 25%]

    Score1 & Score2 & Score3 --> Aggregate[Aggregate Scores]

    UseCache --> CacheResult[Cached Analysis Result]
    Aggregate --> Final[Final Confluence Score]
    CacheResult --> Final

    Final --> Threshold{Score ≥ 65%?}

    Threshold --> |Yes| Signal[Generate Signal]
    Threshold --> |No| NoSignal[No Signal]

    Signal --> Store[Store in Cache]
    NoSignal --> Store

    Store --> End([Analysis Complete])

    %% Styling
    classDef tfBox fill:#e7f5ff,stroke:#1c7ed6,color:#000
    classDef analysis fill:#d3f9d8,stroke:#2f9e44,color:#000
    classDef score fill:#fff4e6,stroke:#f4a127,color:#000
    classDef decision fill:#f8f9fa,stroke:#495057,color:#000

    class ScalpTF,DayTF,SwingTF,PosTF tfBox
    class Analyze1,Analyze2,Analyze3 analysis
    class Score1,Score2,Score3 score
    class Cache,Cache2,Cache3,Cache4,Threshold decision
```

## Timeframe Weighting by Trading Type

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Scalping["Scalping (1-240 min)"]
        M1[M1: 40%]
        M5[M5: 35%]
        M15[M15: 25%]
    end

    subgraph DayTrading["Day Trading (30-1440 min)"]
        M15_2[M15: 30%]
        H1[H1: 40%]
        H4[H4: 30%]
    end

    subgraph SwingTrading["Swing Trading (1-7 days)"]
        H4_2[H4: 35%]
        D1[D1: 40%]
        W1[W1: 25%]
    end

    subgraph PositionTrading["Position Trading (1-4 weeks)"]
        D1_2[D1: 30%]
        W1_2[W1: 45%]
        MN1[MN1: 25%]
    end
```

## Cache Strategy by Trading Type

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Cache["Cache Duration Strategy"]
        direction TB
        ScalpingCache[Scalping: 5 seconds<br/>Fast-paced, frequent updates]
        DayCache[Day Trading: 30 seconds<br/>Balance between speed & freshness]
        SwingCache[Swing Trading: 1 hour<br/>Moderate update frequency]
        PositionCache[Position Trading: 1 day<br/>Long-term analysis sufficient]
    end

    ScalpingCache --> Reason1[Reason: Ultra-short term<br/>Need real-time data]
    DayCache --> Reason2[Reason: Intraday moves<br/>30-min candle frequency]
    SwingCache --> Reason3[Reason: Daily swings<br/>Hourly checks sufficient]
    PositionCache --> Reason4[Reason: Long-term trends<br/>Daily checks adequate]
```
